      • Planet

        public Planet(java.lang.String name,
              java.lang.String state,
              java.lang.String color,
              double radius,
              double speed,
              boolean direct,
              double degree)
        Constructor.
        参数:
        name - planet's name
        state - planet's state
        color - planet's color
        radius - planet's radius, unit is kilometer
        speed - planet's speed, unit is kilometer per second
        direct - planet's revolution direction, true if it's clockwise, false if it's counter-clockwise.
        degree - planet's degree
